                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A4e/625: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1926-07-26T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 26, 1926—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>148. Your 298, July 24, 3 p.m. [<hi rend="italic">a.m.</hi>], 301, July 24, 6
                    p.m. Department approves action taken by you, as stated therein.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
